2014-04-15
   * Added LAMBDA1PATH environment variable to crossval.sh, allowing the use
     of a single file containing the lambda1 path values. Thanks to Marco
     Colombo for patches implementing this feature.

2013-12-16
   * Reverted default scaling of continuous phenotypes (in linear model),
     set the bash argument SCALEY to any non-empty string to enable it, as in 
     SCALEY=yes crossval.sh root linear
